<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>8 SPEED, 9 SPEED, AND 13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - INSTALL - GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>For models equipped with an LRC or SRC Assembly, the housing is installed in the same manner
                    described in the following instructions.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check the shifter housing assembly to make sure shift block and yoke notches are aligned in
                the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cp">Figure 427</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cp" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cp" filename="../figg13/G13018CP.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 426. Make Sure Shift Block and Yoke Notches Are Aligned in Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the new gear shift lever housing gasket in position on the shifter housing and
                install the shift lever housing on the shifter housing, fitting the lever into the shift block and yoke
                notches (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cq">Figure 428</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cq" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cq" filename="../figg13/G13018CQ.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 427. Install Shift Lever Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Loctite 242 to the bolt threads. Install the retaining bolts and tighten to 35 to 45
                ft-lbs. (47 to 61 Nm) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cr">Figure 429</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cr" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cr" filename="../figg13/G13018CR.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 428. Install Retaining Bolts and Tighten</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
